{"tid":2401152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消息：只有9間中學申請全校面授復課","createTime":"2021-02-09T13:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-09T13:56:59.000Z","uid":42188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2abd5b91fec30d3578ff7e90ab04b5fc05eb49f7","tid":2401152,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:29:51.000Z","msg":"邊9間呢？<br />\n各位加油搵出來，然後表揚呢啲校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，若學校安排全體教師定期兩周一檢，持陰性結果的學校可在農曆年假後，全校恢復面授課。消息傳出後引起教育界熱烈討論，中學校長會今日（9日）公布，收集了中學界對新措施的意見，獲全港逾7成（338間）中學回覆，94%學校擬在農曆年假後，每日安排不多於全校三分之一學生回校，當中只有9間中學計劃安排全校教職員定期檢測，以全校復課。"},{"pid":"6499fd166904b4cf65587c0722637b7b48ea1322","tid":2401152,"uid":330227,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺班房入面聽書根本唔會有事<br />\n搭地鐵巴士個個面貼面都未有事啦<br />\n食飯嗰陣唔講嘢同埋飯堂用膠紙隔返開咪得<br />\n恐懼撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1389a8fde7a48a3b154ad13b0f326557725e6236","tid":2401152,"uid":196924,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:36:20.000Z","msg":"成件事根本唔合理<br />\n教職員得幾十個, 學生就幾百個<br />\n接觸嚟講, 又係學生同學生之間最多緊密接觸<br />\n驗教職員做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2dcbf716f338fe5a6be560a25e86592455dbd6","tid":2401152,"uid":254383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:36:35.000Z","msg":"邊狗間官中定紅校"},{"pid":"d657988e1976064d3197df25ac43c9493d8155d6","tid":2401152,"uid":249960,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T13:41:16.000Z","msg":"一個唔小心成間學校嘅人去晒隔離就好笑"},{"pid":"2d242cfb69e6b4748e1aebf7ba46a90dc355ac62","tid":2401152,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"repl